        <updateDate>2019-11-13T16:15:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Senior and Disability Home Modification Assistance Initiative Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Administration on Aging to take a series of actions relating to home modifications that support independent living for older individuals and individuals with disabilities. Specifically, the administration must (1) coordinate, evaluate, and report on existing federal programs that support such home modifications; and (2) publish an educational brochure about such home modifications and available resources.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
